metadata.name: Obedience
metadata.description:
The plot is transparent in the art.
The problem is as old as the world. The problem of domestic violence.
1 out of 2 children (1 billion children) suffer some form of violence each year.
Stranger children are harder to help. But you can help your own child.
I feel very sorry for the girl in the picture. I want to protect her, but I can't.
But I will do everything possible to prevent this from happening to my child.
Being a parent is hard, but it's our choice. A child is a privilege.
Love your children!
